      "comment": "RUN ROLEX (3) was quickly into stride on debut to score by 2 lengths (17.65) at this track over 300m. Rates a top chance again. KINGSBRAE MAGGIE (4) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Sacrifice (18.05) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in the finish again. TULLOCH ROAD (7) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 17.61 beating Little Big Guy. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Should be in this for a long way. THEO THE GREAT (2) in the money here last time and looks a top-three prospect again.",
